## Cara Menjalankan

### 1. Aktifkan virtual environment
```bash
knn_env\Scripts\activate        # Windows
source knn_env/bin/activate     # Linux/Mac
```

### 2. Install dependensi
```bash
pip install django pandas openpyxl scikit-learn
```

### 3. Jalankan server
```bash
python manage.py runserver
```

### 4. Buka dashboard
Buka browser di **http://127.0.0.1:8000/**

### 5. Jalankan analisis via CLI (opsional)
```bash
python src/analisis_kondisi_lingkungan.py
```

